AssetCompress
=============

Provides handy rake tasks to compress assets using YuiCompressor.


Usage
=====

After installing this plugin, do rake -T to view custom rake tasks added by this plugin.

Javascript Compression:

To compress javascript files from your public folder do...

  >> rake yui:all_js_compress

  Output: public/javascripts/compressed.js

Above rake task recursively compress all javascript files from application public/javascripts folder.
  

Stylesheet Compression:

You can compress all stylesheet files using following command...

  >> yui:all_css_compress

  Output: public/stylesheets/compressed.css




